snippet.title: Over My Dead Body (For You) Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Mortiga Scientist Noelle Brody has found herself as the latest subject of a horrible experiment. Now in a state of "Double Undeath" she must fight against her former employers with all that she has. Mind, Body, and Soul.

Coming to Wii U and PC via downloadable platforms.

Please vote for us at Steam Greenlight! Over here http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=710047194 Thank you.
